description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Phang Nga Bay, Thailand
-Mallorca, Spain
-Koh Lipe island, Thailand
-Tenerife, Spain
-Phi Phi Islands, Thailand
-Ko Poda, Thailand
-Porto Rafael, Italy
-Rhodes, Greece
-Anse Source D`argent, Seychelles
-Phi Phi Islands(distant view), Thailand
name: Great View of the Seaside
